/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brian-Fallon-Bruce-Springsteen-696x445.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brian-Fallon-Bruce-Springsteen-1392x891.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brian-Fallon-Bruce-Springsteen-1068x684.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-gaslight-anthem">煤气灯圣歌 (Gaslight Anthem)</a>的主唱布莱恩·法伦 (Brian Fallon) 讲述了他 2009 年第一次见到布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-springsteen">Bruce Springsteen)</a>的经历。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/does-rock-n-roll-kill-braincells-the-gaslight-anthem-brian-fallon-3495130">摇滚乐会杀死脑细胞吗？！ ——《煤气灯颂歌》的布莱恩·法伦</a></strong></li></ul><p>早在七月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gaslight-anthem-share-history-books-feat-bruce-springsteen-and-announce-first-album-in-nine-years-3471572">乐队就宣布了他们九年来的第一张唱片《History Books》</a> ，并分享了主打歌，这是与斯普林斯汀本人的二重唱。在<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/does-rock-n-roll-kill-braincells-the-gaslight-anthem-brian-fallon-3495130"><em>NME 的</em>新采访</a>中，法伦回忆了他对斯普林斯汀<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-161-1320368">加入格拉斯顿伯里乐队</a>表演“The &#39;59 Sound”的反应。</p><p> “我们的比赛还有 10 分钟，所以当他出现时，我无法思考，”法伦说。 “我的音乐专业大脑接管了，因为我的常规大脑吓坏了，我对他说：‘你知道这首歌吗？那我们走吧！这是一个小帐篷，之后感觉非常史诗般。我吓坏了。”</p><p>他继续说道：“我不得不直接回到公交车上，躺在地板上思考：‘到底发生了什么？我现在在俱乐部吗？我现在可以获得卡片或徽章吗？在<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury">格拉斯顿伯</a>里与布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀一起演奏后，我至少应该获得一张 Nando 的黑卡！” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="煤气灯颂歌 - 历史书籍（ft. Bruce Springsteen） - 官方视频" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gyUgfrCegOs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p></p><p>据透露，斯普林斯汀帮助乐队在 2021 年重聚。在与 The Boss 会面后，法伦挑战自己为《煤气灯颂歌》创作四首新歌。</p><p> “我想和自己达成这个协议，因为我觉得如果我打电话给这些人并说：‘你想这样做吗？’你必须有一些东西可以向他们展示，”法伦解释道。 “我想要四个我感觉不错的小样，这几乎是一张专辑的一半。当我完成第一首歌曲《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-gaslight-anthem-return-with-first-new-song-in-nine-years-announce-us-tour-buy-tickets-3437269">Positive Charge</a> 》时，感觉就像一首《Gaslight Anthem》歌曲，属于《45》或《The Sound of &#39;59》旁边的歌曲，并且知道我正在做一些特别的事情。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="煤气灯颂歌 - 正电荷（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Rymbk5I_WlA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>法伦和斯普林斯汀从此变得亲密起来，他在<em>《NME》中进一步拓展了这一点。</em> “布鲁斯是我的朋友，我并没有忘记，我可以说：‘哦，我可以给我的朋友布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀发短信，看看他今晚是否想看一会儿电视！’”他说。</p><p> “他现在录制唱片感觉像是一个完整的循环时刻，拥有我们自己的故事并接受我们是一支来自新泽西的乐队。因为还有来自新泽西的其他乐队，但没有其他乐队能与他一起担任这个职位。我的化学罗曼史是一支比我们全球范围内的乐队大得多的乐队，但布鲁斯叔叔不和他们一起出去玩！”</p><p>布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 (Bruce Springsteen) <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-being-treated-for-peptic-ulcer-disease-symptoms-postpones-all-september-shows-3494366">最近宣布，由于“消化性溃疡病的症状”，他将推迟 9 月份的演出</a>。</p><p>在 X（以前称为 Twitter）上的一系列推文中，他写道：“在 E 街，我们对不得不推迟这些演出感到心碎。首先，向我们几周前错过的出色的费城球迷道歉。我们会回来挑选这些节目，然后再挑选一些。感谢您的理解和支持。”</p><p> <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gaslight-anthem-share-history-books-feat-bruce-springsteen-and-announce-first-album-in-nine-years-3471572">Gaslight Anthem 的新专辑《History Books</a> 》将于 10 月 27 日发行。</em></p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-gaslight-anthem-on-first-meeting-with-bruce-springsteen-i-freaked-out-3498727">《煤气灯颂歌》中关于与布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀第一次见面的帖子：“我吓坏了”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
利佐在持续的法律斗争中接受昆西琼斯人道主义奖https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-accepts-quincy-jones-人道主义-award-amid-ongoing-legal-battles-3502672?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=lizzo-accepts-quincy-jones-持续的法律斗争中的人道主义奖Alex RigottiFri, 22 Sep 2023 15:34:14 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3502672 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-BMAC-Gala.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Lizzo 被她的伴舞 Big Grrls 授予昆西·琼斯人道主义奖。 （约翰尼·努涅斯/盖蒂图片社为黑人音乐行动联盟拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-BMAC-Gala.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-BMAC-Gala-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-BMAC-Gala-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-BMAC-Gala-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-BMAC-Gala-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-BMAC-Gala-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我现在就需要这个。上帝的时间总是准时的！”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-accepts-quincy-jones-humanitarian-award-amidst-ongoing-legal-battles-3502672">利佐在持续的法律斗争中接受昆西·琼斯人道主义奖的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-BMAC-Gala.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Lizzo 被她的伴舞 Big Grrls 授予昆西·琼斯人道主义奖。 （约翰尼·努涅斯/盖蒂图片社为黑人音乐行动联盟拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-BMAC-Gala.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-BMAC-Gala-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-BMAC-Gala-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-BMAC-Gala-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-BMAC-Gala-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-BMAC-Gala-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/?s=lizzo">利佐</a>在另一起诉讼中被点名后不久就接受了昆西琼斯人道主义奖，同时发表的演讲似乎提到了她目前的法律问题。</p><p>周四（9月21日）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-named-in-new-bullying-and-harassment-lawsuit-from-fashion-designer-3502090">利佐遭遇诉讼，称其团队中存在种族歧视、欺凌和骚扰行为</a>。这是近期针对艺术家的第二起诉讼；上个月，她的三名伴舞演员提起诉讼，指控<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-sued-by-backup-dancers-for-sexual-harassment-and-creating-hostile-work-environment-3476570">这位歌手对她的舞者进行性骚扰，并创造了一个充满敌意的工作环境</a>等。</p><p>但昨天，针对利佐的团队提出了新的欺凌指控。 Lizzo 的前时装设计师阿莎·丹尼尔斯 (Asha Daniels) 声称，Lizzo 的服装经理阿曼达·野村 (Amanda Nomura) 称伴舞演员“胖”、“无用”和“愚蠢”。野村还被指控对黑人女性留下刻板印象，并强迫她们在以白人为主的男性工作人员面前做出改变，而这些工作人员会“下流地盯着”舞者。</p><p>丹尼尔斯的律师罗恩·赞布拉诺说：“利佐是老板，所以责任由她承担。” </p><figure id="attachment_3502710" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3502710" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3502710" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-BMAC-Gala-2.jpg" alt="利佐在 BMAC 晚会上接受昆西·琼斯人道主义奖。 （约翰尼·努涅斯/盖蒂图片社为黑人音乐行动联盟拍摄）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-BMAC-Gala-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-BMAC-Gala-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-BMAC-Gala-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-BMAC-Gala-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-BMAC-Gala-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-BMAC-Gala-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3502710" class="wp-caption-text">利佐在 BMAC 晚会上接受昆西·琼斯人道主义奖。 （约翰尼·努涅斯/盖蒂图片社为黑人音乐行动联盟拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p>当天晚些时候，利佐出席了黑人音乐行动联盟晚会，接受了昆西·琼斯人道主义奖。尽管她没有出现在黑地毯上，但她确实登上了舞台，接受了一些伴舞者的颁奖，这些伴舞者统称为“Big Grrls”和“Big Boiis”。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzos-big-grrl-dancers-praise-her-for-shattering-limitations-in-new-open-letter-3484966">此前，一些舞者曾在 8 月 18 日写的一封公开信中赞扬过这位歌手</a>。</p><p>在观看了 Lizzo 之前支持 LGBTQ+ 权利和计划生育组织的人道主义努力的视频剪辑后，这位歌手发表了讲话。</p><p> “ <a id="auto-tag_black-music-action-coalition" href="https://variety.com/t/black-music-action-coalition/" data-tag="black-music-action-coalition">黑人音乐行动联盟</a>，你们真的很关心这个行动，”她开始说道。 “非常感谢你，因为我现在需要这个。神的时间总是准时的！ I didn&#39;t write a speech because I don&#39;t know what to say in times like these.”</p><p> After speaking about her history of philanthropy, she continued: “It&#39;s easy to do the right thing when everybody&#39;s watching you, and it&#39;s what you do in those moments when nobody&#39;s watching that defines who you are. And I&#39;m going to continue to be who I am, no matter who&#39;s watching. I&#39;m going to continue to shine a light on the people who are helping people, because they deserve it. I&#39;m going to continue to amplify the voices of marginalized people because I have a microphone and I know how to use it.”</p><p> “And, I&#39;m going to continue to put on and represent safe spaces for fat Black women, because that&#39;s what the fuck I do!” </p><figure id="attachment_3502711" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3502711" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3502711" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-Flava-Flav-BMAC-Gala.jpg" alt="Lizzo poses with Flava Flav at the BMAC Gala 2023. (Photo by Johnny Nunez/Getty Images for Black Music Action Coalition)" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-Flava-Flav-BMAC-Gala.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-Flava-Flav-BMAC-Gala-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-Flava-Flav-BMAC-Gala-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-Flava-Flav-BMAC-Gala-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-Flava-Flav-BMAC-Gala-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lizzo-Flava-Flav-BMAC-Gala-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3502711" class="wp-caption-text"> Lizzo poses with Flava Flav at the BMAC Gala 2023. (Photo by Johnny Nunez/Getty Images for Black Music Action Coalition)</figcaption></figure><p> So far, Lizzo has denied all claims brought by both lawsuits. <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-named-in-new-bullying-and-harassment-lawsuit-from-fashion-designer-3502090https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-named-in-new-bullying-and-harassment-lawsuit-from-fashion-designer-3502090">A spokesperson for Lizzo responded to the most recent lawsuit</a> , calling it “a bogus, absurd publicity-stunt” from a person who “never actually met or even spoke with Lizzo.”</p><p> They further added: “We will pay this as much attention as it deserves.没有任何。”</p><p> Lizzo also personally responded to the original lawsuit on August 3, where <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-responds-to-sexual-harassment-lawsuit-im-hurt-3477714">she wrote a lengthy Instagram post</a> . “Usually I choose not to respond to false allegations but these are as unbelievable as they sound and too outrageous to not be addressed,” she said. “I&#39;m hurt but I will not let the good work I&#39;ve done in the world be overshadowed by this.”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-planning-to-sue-former-backup-dancers-for-malicious-prosecution-3487885">Lizzo is also planning on suing the original three dancers</a> for “malicious prosecution”. The singer&#39;s attorney Martin Singer, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-hires-former-billy-cosby-lawyer-for-sexual-harassment-lawsuit-3478228">who has previously represented clinets such as Bill Cosby and Johnny Depp</a> , has called the lawsuit a “sham”.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-accepts-quincy-jones-humanitarian-award-amidst-ongoing-legal-battles-3502672">Lizzo accepts Quincy Jones Humanitarian Award amidst ongoing legal battles</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
